{"tid":128960,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【回帶】小飛象有力試衝＄78","createTime":"2017-02-21T08:46:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-21T13:09:28.000Z","uid":26619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6b344741a4313116c79df4a45e9f39c09e967aac","tid":128960,"uid":26619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T08:46:28.000Z","msg":"[本地] 23小時前<br />\n【Now財經台】滙豐控股( 00005 )股價今早平開後，曾短暫倒跌，曾低見68.1元，其後重拾升勢，午後在成交急增下，升幅顯著擴大，股價最高見69.1元，最終以近全日高位69元收市，升逾1%。<br />\n滙控將於明日派發去年成績表，有券商看淡集團業績，預期滙控去年稅前盈利最多倒退30%，除核心業務外，市場亦關注集團會否再有回購計劃。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，自滙控去年中宣布推出25億美元股份回購計劃後，股價自40元水平，逐步升至現時逼近70元，累升逾50%，以2015年「大時代」高位，以及去年低位延伸的黃金比率計算，滙控股價已突破0.618，後市有機會上望78元水平。<br />\n<br />\n信NOW班財演一成都死，都係大師最老實。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8bc64956a0501fb5e319a16f22cdf1358321a1d","tid":128960,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T08:48:49.000Z","msg":"53蚊先諗"},{"pid":"78b16b4fb1fb5cea9fad176f29cef773da2614a3","tid":128960,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T08:55:54.000Z","msg":"28 再考慮"},{"pid":"413cc06e4a6dc069dadc1fe6a4df3c9d761a883f","tid":128960,"uid":24570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T09:06:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91b16dea30ccf66acb52e2dd90c08c746c0cf673","tid":128960,"uid":5537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T09:18:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>53蚊先諗</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nVicF師兄 做咩今日唔番沈門？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c6b38cc6947e73d96a1397b54d20b610c054153","tid":128960,"uid":72647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T09:27:00.000Z","msg":"落返45蚊先入"},{"pid":"ce39f8d745703096bf7ba83e478f4b17fe20b64d","tid":128960,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T09:32:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote